{"1":[[333,446,"Ms. Gray,"],[446,650,"I'm sorry, but the chances of you"],[650,746,"getting pregnant on your own"],[746,892,"are near zero."],[1013,1176,"God. Why?"],[1176,1476,"Why are you so cruel to me?"],[1497,1714,"I lost my parents when I was young,"],[1714,1818,"and now I'll never even be"],[1818,1989,"a parent myself."],[1989,2173,"There is no need to despair."],[2173,2364,"Infertility is still treatable."],[2364,2552,"Really? Yes."],[2552,2740,"In your situation,"],[2740,2852,"the easiest way to get pregnant"],[2852,2994,"is through artificial insemination."],[3061,3290,"The only thing is, it's a bit expensive."],[3328,3553,"Um, well"],[3553,3757,"I’ll have to talk it over with my fiancé"],[3757,3820,"but um"],[3820,4058,"I’m sure he’ll support me"],[5292,5388,"Tony?"],[5538,5860,"Leia why are you here?"],[5860,6006,"Babe, who’s this?"],[6293,6514,"She uhhh, She's that one ex"],[6514,6602,"I told you about."],[6602,6785,"The clingy one who's broke"],[6785,6902,"and can't have kids."],[7057,7290,"Ex? You just proposed to me"],[7290,7407,"two weeks ago."],[7415,7545,"Since when am I your ex?"],[7545,7670,"You proposed to her?"],[7670,7824,"Of course I didn't she..."],[7824,7962,"she threatened to kill herself"],[7962,8124,"if I didn't get back together with her."],[8158,8220,"So I felt bad."],[8220,8400,"I gave her a stupid little ring."],[8400,8445,"What?"],[8508,8558,"Look at her."],[8558,8833,"She's a infertile orphan girl."],[8833,8963,"Why would I marry her?"],[8963,9079,"Your outfit probably cost more"],[9079,9255,"than her whole net worth."],[9255,9442,"You are such a liar."],[9442,9743,"That is not what happened at all."],[9843,9939,"Bitch"],[9939,10068,"You think I would have ever offered"],[10068,10139,"to marry you"],[10139,10352,"if you hadn't lent me that 50 grand?"],[10352,10456,"Fuck off, Leia,"],[10531,10623,"I only dated you"],[10623,10769,"because I felt sorry for you."],[10769,10952,"I'm with Amanda, and we're engaged."],[11006,11144,"And y