 event."],[8504,8562,"Please."],[8625,8687,"You’re going to be the one"],[8687,8846,"out-classing me."],[8867,9021,"Shall we,"],[9021,9100,"my queen?"]],"23":[[304,475,"Well, that settles it, George."],[475,550,"It is a pleasure"],[550,654,"to have you on the project."],[654,763,"Alec."],[763,1059,"I got a friend that's dying to meet you."],[1209,1297,"Come with me!"],[1297,1368,"N--, Now?"],[1368,1626,"Yes yes yes."],[1659,1805,"Whew, we finally locked in"],[1805,1914,"the new investor."],[1914,2052,"Now I can exhale."],[2052,2281,"Damn, I’m hungry."],[2281,2427,"Let’s go see where the food’s at."],[3328,3449,"Umm..."],[3478,3561,"Hello?"],[3607,3703,"Oh. I'm sorry."],[3703,3828,"You go first."],[4041,4191,"Hey. You look familiar."],[4191,4333,"Do I know you from somewhere?"],[4333,4483,"You look familiar too."],[4483,4592,"Ahhh we must have"],[4592,4746,"met somewhere before."],[4746,4788,"Let's see."],[4788,5034,"Do you, remember my name?"],[5234,5380,"Well, in case you forgot,"],[5380,5534,"it's Xavier Holland."],[5538,5789,"Oh. Oh, Xavier Holland. Yeah."],[5789,6018,"You're that famous actor, right?"],[6018,6110,"I read that you're, like,"],[6110,6239,"the highest paid celebrity"],[6239,6335,"in Hollywood right now."],[6352,6531,"Bingo. And you?"],[6564,6673,"I'm Leia Gray."],[6673,6790,"I'm the manager of marketing"],[6790,6952,"operations over at Lawrence Group."],[6952,7111,"If my memory serves me right,"],[7111,7261,"you are our spokesperson"],[7261,7390,"for next quarter, huh?"],[7390,7549,"Well, I look forward to working with you."],[7811,7966,"I look forward to a partnership."],[7966,8174,"Oh, I'm not really drinking right now."],[8174,8279,"Oh, why is that?"],[8279,8370,"Because she's pregnant."]],"24":[[41,258,"Are you guys, uhh a thing?"],[379,504,"We live together."],[504,600,"Alec!"],[713,809,"What?"],[809,892,"It's true."],[896,971,"You’re going to give people"],[971,1105,"the wrong idea about us."],[1176,1317,"Are you a couple or..?"],[1317,1430,"