ookie, get down from there!"],[859,1005,"Mr. Lawrence has OCD."],[1005,1055,"He’ll freak out"],[1055,1167,"if he sees you on there."],[1167,1326,"He'll kick us out of the house."],[1326,1539,"Get out, Cookie! Get out."],[1659,1747,"Hey..."],[2206,2435,"Leia"],[2435,2581,"I want to kiss you."],[2752,3053,"So kiss me."],[5055,5263,"Wait. wait"]],"28":[[450,667,"No..."],[667,734,"wait!"],[734,1034,"I have to feed Cookie."],[1213,1359,"Bad dog!"],[1359,1472,"I feed you every day"],[1472,1722,"and this is how you repay me?"],[2243,2560,"No, I really have to feed Cookie."],[2702,2811,"I'm going to need another shower"],[2811,2952,"after this anyway."],[4358,4462,"Cut!"],[4617,4767,"Xavier,"],[4767,4950,"Cindy is supposed to be your girlfriend."],[5021,5092,"Can you at least show"],[5092,5180,"a bit of interest in her?"],[5246,5309,"Dammit, kid,"],[5309,5459,"I've seen people look more lovingly"],[5459,5572,"at a pile of dog shit."],[5776,6001,"Me and Cindy have no chemistry."],[6110,6227,"Could we replace her?"],[6598,6898,"How about... her?"],[7173,7303,"With her, I won't even have to act."]],"29":[[0,200,"She does have that..."],[200,321,"main character aura."],[408,558,"All right you, get over there."],[558,842,"But no no no no no, I'm not an actress."],[842,925,"You should definitely"],[925,1021,"ask someone else."],[1021,1226,"Leia, are you crazy?"],[1226,1397,"Xavier fucking Holland wants"],[1397,1543,"to film a commercial with you."],[1551,1693,"You just don’t say no to that."],[1693,1805,"Just do it, Leia!"],[1805,1897,"The sooner we finish,"],[1897,2027,"the sooner we go home."],[2256,2335,"Ok."],[2414,2594,"Well, well, well."],[2594,2773,"We meet again."],[2773,2940,"Don't act like this is some coincidence."],[2940,3090,"I know you were the one who requested"],[3090,3240,"that I supervise this shoot."],[3294,3516,"I know you're not with Alec."],[3516,3787,"And I know that child isn't his either."],[3787,3937,"Yeah, yeah. You're right."],[3966,4141,"But I don't know why"],[4141,4254,"it’s any of your business."],[4254,4337,"It's my business..."],[4337,4546,"because that means"],[4546,4658,"we can do whatever we want."],[4917,5000,"Perfect."],[5000,5113,"Hold that pose."],[5113,5288,"That's what I'm looking for!"],[5288,5434,"And action!"]],"30":[[246,362,"Don't be scared."],[362,417,"Let’s just do"],[417,542,"whatever the director says."],[642,788,"Give me the fireworks sounds."],[804,938,"Ok, Xavier and Leia,"],[938,1155,"when the fireworks go off,"],[1155,1259,"I need you to kiss."],[1326,1593,"Kiss? Oh, no no, no I can't do that."],[1593,1664,"No. It's okay."],[1664,1722,"No no no."],[1722,1822,"I got this."],[2494,2623,"Cut!"],[2623,2794,"Yes!!"],[3028,3236,"What the hell is going on here?"],[3395,3695,"Mr. Lawrence, Leia saved our shoot."],[3712,3862,"She and Xavier are"],[3862,3966,"a match made in heaven."],[3966,4058,"This commercial..."],[4058,4312,"is going to be a huge hit."],[4450,4625,"You heard the man."],[4625,4925,"Guess we look like a real couple."],[5013,5288,"It is your job to find the right actors."],[5288,5434,"If something like this happens again,"],[5434,5547,"it will be the last commercial"],[5547,5634,"you ever shoot."],[5634,5780,"Do you understand me?"],[5780,5868,"Come with me."],[5868,5989,"What are you doing?"]],"31":[[0,175,"What’re you doing?"],[1055,1201,"I've worked here for four years,"],[1201,1309,"and I've never seen"],[1309,1463,"Mr. Lawrence this upset."],[1501,1743,"Leia must have really screwed up."],[1743,1901,"Think they're fighting in there?"],[1901,2202,"Maybe. Wait!"],[2214,2364,"Whose side are we on?"],[2602,2731,"Stop it! You’re hurting me."],[2873,3069,"Why did you kiss Xavier?"],[3069,3199,"You like him?"],[3199,3324,"You got a thing for man whores"],[3324,3386,"like him?"],[3386,3465,"Is that it?"],[3465,3674,"Alec, I’m in charge of this shoot."],[3674,3782,"Xavier wasn't getting along"],[3782,3845,"with his costar."],[3845,3933,"He asked me to fill in."],[3933,4074,"What w