you do?"],[1126,1347,"You managed your coworker"],[1347,1484,"straight into your bedroom."],[1484,1776,"Jeez, Mom, don't say it like that."],[1776,1885,"Leia and I have feelings"],[1885,1951,"for each other..."],[1951,2114,"but it's not getting in the way of work."],[2139,2285,"Yeah, sure."],[2285,2389,"Look at you."],[2389,2644,"Renting out this entire place."],[2723,2840,"You're going to propose to her"],[2840,2969,"tonight, aren't you?"],[2969,3140,"Yes, Mother, I am."],[3140,3449,"No, I will not let that happen!"],[3499,3649,"I read up on her."],[3649,3908,"She is an orphan."],[3908,4012,"Her ex left her because"],[4012,4149,"she couldn't get pregnant."],[4149,4287,"And now she's going to have a"],[4312,4475,"sperm donor baby."],[4504,4667,"If you put a ring on her finger,"],[4667,4892,"our family will be the laughing stock"],[4892,5042,"of the entire social elite."],[5042,5088,"Mom,"],[5146,5309,"Leia is the one that I want and..."],[5472,5651,"and I don't care what you think."],[5689,5814,"So you're choosing her"],[5814,5960,"over our family?"],[6010,6093,"That wicked woman."],[6093,6314,"She's got you blinded by love."],[6314,6456,"You think you can be a father"],[6456,6614,"to her baby?"],[6627,6777,"I'm not letting you pass our"],[6777,6923,"inheritance down to"],[6923,7061,"a bastard child."],[7073,7207,"It’s not a bastard..."],[7232,7357,"I'm the father!"]],"35":[[0,166,"Alec, tell me what's going on."],[166,300,"Leia!"],[308,608,"Leia, the sperm donor..."],[746,875,"It was me."],[875,1013,"No."],[1013,1113,"I'm- I'm sorry."],[1113,1188,"I didn't mean to hide it"],[1188,1309,"from you like this."],[1309,1447,"So you’ve been..."],[1447,1726,"you've been lying to me all this time?"],[1885,2010,"You got me pregnant"],[2010,2118,"with your baby."],[2118,2314,"You pretended. You-"],[2314,2498,"You pretended to care about me."],[2498,2706,"You moved me into your house."],[2706,2886,"All so that I would fall in love with you."],[2886,3140,"Leia it's not like that. Okay?"],[3140,3353,"If I hadn't overheard you just now,"],[3353,3470,"you would have kept it from me"],[3470,3541,"forever. Leia-"],[3541,3682,"take deep breaths, all right?"],[3682,3849,"You can't get overworked"],[3849,3983,"in this condition."],[4262,4312,"Well,"],[4312,4462,"it's a relief to know that you"],[4462,4621,"won't be raising someone else's kid."],[4704,4808,"I have no problem with you"],[4808,4904,"giving a pregnant woman"],[4904,5005,"a place to stay."],[5021,5092,"But..."],[5092,5209,"after she gives birth, you're"],[5209,5313,"just going to give her some money"],[5313,5434,"and send her on her way."],[5434,5718,"Are you insane, Mother?"],[5718,5893,"I would never do that."],[6172,6285,"I love her..."]],"36":[[150,254,"Get out of my way!"],[254,333,"I'm not moving..."],[333,496,"until you let me explain myself."],[496,625,"What is there to explain?"],[625,784,"It’s just like your Mother said -"],[784,1009,"you tricked me into having this baby,"],[1009,1117,"and once the baby’s born"],[1117,1238,"you’re just going to find some excuse"],[1238,1426,"to get rid of me and steal my kid."],[1488,1597,"You’re a total scumbag."],[1735,1856,"Leia!"],[1856,2097,"It's not true. Leia..."],[2097,2210,"I have liked you since the moment"],[2210,2348,"you started working"],[2348,2489,"for Lawrence Group."],[2489,2631,"I've never lied to you"],[2631,2802,"or tried to play any tricks on you."],[2894,3082,"It was Jerry who told them"],[3082,3161,"to give you my sperm."],[3161,3290,"I didn't know about until"],[3290,3461,"after your procedure."],[3474,3570,"And I-"],[3570,3762,"I didn't tell you because..."],[3762,3999,"well, I didn't think you liked me."],[3999,4120,"You told me that you wanted to"],[4120,4287,"raise the baby alone."],[4358,4583,"I know that you deserve the truth."],[4583,4746,"I was going to explain"],[4746,4884,"everything tonight."],[4896,5105,"Alec, I'm not stupid."],[5105,5205,"Why should I believe you"],[5205,5376,"after all of this?"],[5609,5784,"If you have any respect for me"],[5784,6068,"at all, whatsoever,"],[6068,6247,"you’ll let me leave."]],"37":[[329,392,"Hey..."],[392,596,"Oh. What happened?"],[596,688,"Don't cry."],[688,838,"Honey."],[946,1197,"God, you've been through so much."],[1197,1292,"My poor girl."],[1459,1576,"I don't even know how"],[1576,1772,"I can face Alec after all of this."],[1822,1910,"I mean, I don't even want"],[1910,2022,"to go into work."],[2085,2293,"But he's the father of my child,"],[2293,2419,"whether I like it or not."],[2419,2635,"Don't quit your job over this."],[2635,2761,"You can't raise a child"],[2761,2936,"as an unemployed, single mother."],[3015,3303,"And after you give it some time..."],[3303,3490,"I think you should hear Alec out."],[3553,3666,"You're my best friend,"],[3666,3849,"you're supposed to take my side."],[3849,4099,"I'm not saying you have to forgive him."],[4099,4295,"It's just that if he was"],[4295,4466,"using you and lying to you,"],[4466,4621,"why would he stick up for you"],[4621,4763,"in front of his mom like that?"],[5030,5113,"I don't care."],[5209,5301,"I don't even want anything"],[5301,5405,"to do with him right now."]],"38":[[725,850,"Jasmine, could I have another one?"],[850,934,"Ah-ah no."],[934,1051,"No, sorry, he’s uhh..."],[1188,1280,"he’s hammered."],[1280,1343,"The last thing he needs right now"],[1343,1393,"is another."],[1393,1514,"C’mon, boss, let’s go home."],[1518,1710,"Jerry, Leia left me."],[1710,1830,"I shouldn’t have waited so long"],[1830,1964,"to tell her the truth."],[1985,2118,"I fucked it up, Jerry."],[2118,2339,"No, boss, this one is on me, okay?"],[2394,2581,"We are gonna get you home."],[2932,3148,"Let’s go: 3, 2, 1. up!"],[3148,3253,"Goodbye, Jasmine."],[3891,4054,"Oh god.."],[4054,4212,"Here, what is it?"],[4212,4366,"Why did she leave me?"],[4366,4642,"Jerry? Why did she go?"],[4696,4842,"I’m so cold..."],[5201,5317,"Let’s get your temperature, Boss,"],[5317,5405,"right here."],[5897,5993,"103 degress??"],[6089,6197,"Okay, Boss,"],[6197,6364,"Boss, you have a bad fever!"],[6423,6564,"Leia!"],[6564,6673,"Leia, where are you?"]],"39":[[759,871,"Leia."],[1067,1230,"I'm here to apologize."],[1426,1568,"Leia..."],[1568,1693,"it was me."],[1805,1981,"I was the one who"],[1981,2110,"called the sperm bank"],[2110,2173,"and told them"],[2173,2331,"to sell you Mr. Lawrence’s sperm."],[2398,2523,"I'm so sorry."],[2556,2727,"Ha! Alec put you up to this, didn't he?"],[2727,2852,"No!"],[2852,2986,"He doesn't even have any idea"],[2986,3048,"that I'm here."],[3182,3424,"Look, I watched him..."],[3424,3682,"pine after you for three years"],[3682,3837,"without ever telling you how he felt."],[3899,4175,"I didn't want him to suffer anymore, so..."],[4175,4291,"I-, I did this..."],[4400,4608,"thinking that it would help him."],[4671,4979,"He's liked me for three years?"]],"40":[[83,325,"He's liked me for three years?"],[325,504,"He's never given me any hints."],[504,658,"I know."],[658,754,"You had a boyfriend"],[754,930,"and he didn't want to overstep, but..."],[963,1142,"but after he found out what I did,"],[1142,1313,"he wanted to tell you straight away."],[1359,1576,"I convinced him not to."],[1659,1835,"Great. I mean, you were looking out..."],[1835,2018,"for your friend, but did you ever"],[2018,2135,"think about me?"],[2218,2364,"Look..."],[2364,2531,"I just thought that since you were"],[2531,2677,"already looking for a sperm donor,"],[2677,2823,"that Mr. Lawrence would be better"],[2823,2907,"than some stranger."],[2998,3219,"And if you ever fall on hard times"],[3219,3378,"in the future, he can make sure"],[3378,3574,"that you and the child are taken care of."],[3724,3937,"I just thought that it would be the best"],[3937,4004,"for everyone."],[4149,4283,"You have no right to make decisions"],[4283,4412,"about other people's lives."],[4412,4679,"I know, but I don't expect"],[4679,4825,"you to forgive me."],[4929,5063,"But I just need you to know that"],[5063,5180,"Mr. Lawrence wasn't trying"],[5180,5276,"to hurt you."],[5342,5505,"Look, all I ask is that"],[5505,5609,"you give him another chance."],[5609,5818,"Or at least go talk to him."],[5880,6051,"Leia, he has a bad fever."],[6147,6268,"He won't stop calling your name."],[6268,6473,"And it's really ..."],[6473,6539,"starting to worry me."],[6539,6585,"Wait-"],[6585,6673,"Alec is sick??"]],"41":[[1255,1393,"Leia!"],[1488,1618,"Please don’t-"],[1618,1914,"Don’t leave- don’t leave me."],[2452,2560,"Here."],[2744,2852,"Sit up."],[3841,4087,"Is this a dream?"],[4124,4304,"Did you really come back?"],[4312,4550,"Why don't you get some rest?"],[4550,4688,"In the morning, you'll find out"],[4688,4800,"if it was a dream."],[5050,5301,"Oh God! What was Jerry thinking"],[5301,5476,"putting you in this shirt?"],[5709,5922,"He’d make a terrible nurse."],[6431,6602,"Alec,"],[6602,6727,"I need to take your shirt off."],[6727,6806,"It’s all sweaty."],[6806,7061,"I need to get you in some clean clothes."],[8754,8938,"Leia..."],[9121,9421,"What’re you- what’re you doing?"]],"42":[[400,525,"Leia, I’m so sorry."],[525,625,"What’re you doing?"],[663,930,"Leia, I didn’t mean to hurt you."],[930,1030,"I wanted to tell you"],[1030,1130,"as soon as I found out"],[1130,1230,"that I was the father."],[1230,1309,"Leia..."],[1309,1609,"please, please forgive me."],[1768,1939,"Fine,"],[1939,2035,"I forgive you."],[2193,2318,"But if something like this"],[2318,2385,"ever happens again,"],[2385,2602,"you won't get another chance."],[2602,2798,"I hate when people lie to me."],[3732,3966,"Hey."],[3966,4179,"Smells good."],[4225,4350,"You're up already?"],[4350,4550,"You had a 103 fever last night."],[4550,4783,"Yeah, well, I got a good sleep, and I- uhh..."],[4967,5255,"I guess something made me feel better."],[5255,5472,"Hey, were you faking being sick"],[5472,5630,"just to make me feel bad for you?"],[5630,5830,"No, I promise you, I'm not faking it."],[5830,6043,"Cross my heart and hope to die."],[6193,6293,"Leia..."],[6352,6544,"I wanted to ask you something..."],[6577,6664,"Yeah?"],[6731,6973,"My Mom just got back from overseas..."],[6973,7215,"and she’s throwing a big party."],[7215,7323,"I wondered if you"],[7323,7428,"wanted to go with me?"],[7636,7807,"I want to take this opportunity to"],[7807,7895,"announce to everyone"],[7895,7982,"that we're engaged."],[8033,8158,"I think when she sees how serious"],[8158,8295,"I am about you,"],[8295,8445,"she'll leave us alone."],[8558,8708,"Sounds like a plan."]],"43":[[583,788,"Who is that with Mr. Lawrence?"],[863,1092,"She's gorgeous."],[1092,1267,"Why haven’t I seen her before?"],[1267,1401,"Is she his future wife?"],[1401,1522,"She has to be."],[1522,1643,"Look at how Mr. Lawrence"],[1643,1735,"is smiling at her."],[1735,1897,"I've literally never"],[1897,2060,"seen him smile at anyone."],[2156,2248,"Damn."],[2268,2510,"She’s a stunner, Clara."],[2510,2606,"You’re lucky at landing"],[2606,2698,"a daughter-in-law like that."],[2698,2819,"What family is she from?"],[2819,2957,"Which family?"],[2957,3219,"She doesn't even have a family."],[3219,3365,"That woman is just"],[3365,3528,"a useless surrogate mother."],[3528,3678,"She’s got some nerve"],[3678,3845,"showing up to my party"],[3845,4012,"like she owns the damn place."],[4295,4387,"Alec,"],[4387,4517,"are you out of your mind?"],[4517,4796,"This woman doesn't belong at my party."],[4796,4879,"Do you know"],[4879,4996,"how this makes me look?"],[5021,5109,"Mom,"],[5109,5238,"I told you already..."],[5238,5413,"I love Leia."],[5442,5647,"She's pregnant with my child,"],[5668,5855,"And I'm going to marry her."],[6085,6277,"Ow. I am warning you-"],[6277,6523,"you keep clinging to my son like this,"],[6523,6748,"and it is not going to end well for you."],[6773,6915,"Mrs. Lawrence please let go of me."],[6915,7007,"Mom,"],[7007,7098,"let her go."],[7228,7403,"You hurt her, you hurt me."],[7403,7653,"The son I know would never"],[7653,7736,"lay hands on me"],[7736,7928,"over some worthless bitch."],[7953,8045,"Go ahead,"],[8045,8128,"marry her,"],[8128,8354,"but the Lawrence family will never"],[8354,8550,"recognize her as one of our own."],[8608,8742,"Yeah, well, we'll see about that"],[8742,8825,"won’t we?"]],"44":[[479,613,"Hello, everyone."],[613,721,"Now, I know we've all gathered here"],[721,771,"to welcome my mother back"],[771,1038,"to the States, However..."],[1201,1276,"I have another special"],[1276,1384,"announcement."],[1480,1705,"Don't worry. It is good news."],[1705,2085,"This is Leia Gray, my fiancée."],[2173,2406,"We're having a baby together!"],[2406,2552,"Whoo-hoo!"],[2748,2827,"Yay!"],[2827,2948,"Kiss, kiss!"],[3232,3424,"Daddy!"],[4170,4404,"Long time no see, Alec."]],"45":[[37,208,"Daddy!"],[342,529,"Alec that little girl"],[529,642,"just called you “daddy”."],[646,900,"Okay, so let me get this straight."],[900,1151,"His current bae is pregnant,"],[1151,1217,"and now his ex"],[1217,1363,"shows up with his kid"],[1363,1480,"trying to get him back?"],[1518,1672,"That's scandalous!"],[1672,1822,"Is his new fiancée still going to"],[1822,2010,"want to marry him now?"],[2010,2193,"Her baby and this other kid"],[2193,2381,"will have to grow up together"],[2381,2590,"and fight over the family fortune."],[2615,2769,"That could get ugly!"],[2769,3065,"Congrats, Clara! You’re a grandma!"],[3103,3286,"What a pleasant surprise this is."],[3328,3432,"I'm sorry,"],[3432,3549,"but I'm not your father."],[3570,3762,"I don't have any children."],[3820,3912,"You're wrong,"],[3912,4024,"Alec."],[4049,4208,"Esther is your daughter."],[4212,4333,"After we broke up seven years ago"],[4333,4600,"I found out I was pregnant, but..."],[4600,4754,"we were so young."],[4754,4954,"I didn't want to tell you."],[4954,5084,"So I decided to raise her"],[5084,5171,"on my own."],[5221,5459,"You were pregnant then, hmm?"],[5459,5593,"I'm sorry, Beatrice,"],[5593,5672,"but I don't believe you."],[5801,5972,"The whole reason that we broke up"],[5972,6076,"was because you were always"],[6076,6243,"lying to me."],[6243,6377,"I'm going to need proof."]],"46":[[746,980,"Wow, he really is the father!"],[1881,1993,"Wait."],[2102,2335,"What a special day this is!"],[2335,2485,"Today, the Lawrences"],[2485,2594,"welcome a new heiress"],[2594,2690,"into the family."],[2731,2927,"Alec, my son, and Beatrice..."],[3057,3236,"are engaged."],[3236,3445,"And the two of them will be raising"],[3445,3741,"Esther together."],[4462,4546,"Leia..."],[5392,5618,"I didn't know about the kid."],[5618,5751,"I haven't seen Beatrice"],[5751,5897,"in seven years."],[5897,6156,"I know you don't love Beatrice,"],[6156,6281,"but Esther is your daughter."],[6343,6452,"At the very least,"],[6452,6585,"you have to play some role"],[6585,6648,"in her life."],[6806,6952,"Alec..."],[6952,7132,"I need some time to myself."]],"47":[[500,704,"So this will be your new home."],[704,813,"I'll make sure the two of you"],[813,938,"have everything you need."],[938,1142,"Thank you, Mrs. Lawrence."],[1142,1330,"You've been so kind to us."],[1330,1630,"Oh, it's the least I could do."],[1630,1780,"I should thank you"],[1780,1889,"for giving birth to such a pretty"],[1889,2110,"little heiress of the Lawrence family."],[2135,2289,"I don't know what Alec sees"],[2289,2385,"in that bitch Leia-"],[2544,2627,"you’re the one"],[2627,2781,"that he should be marrying."],[2781,2844,"Mom,"],[2898,3036,"me and Leia live here."],[3036,3199,"You can't just bring people over"],[3199,3324,"whenever you like."],[3324,3436,"“People”?"],[3436,3541,"They're your daughter"],[3541,3695,"and your daughter's mother."],[3695,3824,"Accept it, Alec -"],[3824,3978,"this is your family."],[3978,4133,"The only one who needs to leave"],[4195,4337,"is that pregnant whore."],[4346,4571,"I told you, I love Leia."],[4571,4704,"I'm going to marry her."],[4800,4954,"She's not going anywhere."],[5759,5847,"Daddy!"],[5847,5972,"Daddy! Why don't you"],[5972,6106,"want me and Mommy?"],[6106,6343,"Did we do something wrong?"],[6560,6715,"I’ll try harder to make you happy Daddy,"],[6715,6777,"Daddy,"],[6777,6952,"just don’t make us go!"]],"48":[[0,125,"Look what you did, Alec!"],[125,316,"Some father you are!"],[316,513,"Don't cry."],[513,613,"Grandma is going to take you"],[613,750,"to go get some candy, okay?"],[934,1109,"Show us to your sweets."],[1109,1343,"Yes, Mother."],[1634,1801,"Would you look at that."],[1801,1968,"He was standing up for you"],[1968,2139,"until my daughter started crying,"],[2193,2398,"then he just forgot you existed."],[2398,2548,"You know nothing about"],[2548,2698,"my relationship with Alec."],[2731,2986,"You're an infertile surrogate mother."],[2986,3069,"What makes you think"],[3069,3211,"you can compete with me?"],[3211,3411,"I am Alec’s first love,"],[3411,3524,"and my daughter"],[3524,3820,"is the heiress of the Lawrence family."],[3820,3962,"It's over."],[3962,4062,"Now get lost."]],"49":[[700,784,"Bad dog!"],[784,934,"Your owner’s a mean lady."],[934,1017,"Go away,"],[1017,1172,"we don't want you here!"],[1455,1555,"Waaahhhh."],[1555,1747,"Mommy! Oh my God."],[1747,1989,"Baby, you're hurt!"],[1989,2106,"Tell Mommy what happened."],[2106,2206,"It was the dog!"],[2206,2402,"It barked at me and tried to bite me."],[2402,2565,"Mommy it hurts."],[2565,2669,"Cookie’s a good dog,"],[2669,2806,"he would never try to hurt you."],[2861,3011,"Did you maybe do something"],[3011,3128,"to upset him?"],[3128,3261,"Don't touch her."],[3261,3361,"It's already enough that"],[3361,3545,"your dog attacked her."],[3545,3774,"Get out of my sight!"],[3924,4016,"Beatrice!"]],"50":[[58,258,"She's pregnant."],[258,392,"That's why she trained"],[392,508,"that beast of an animal"],[508,684,"to attack Esther."],[684,834,"I cannot touch you because you’re"],[834,992,"pregnant with Alec’s child,"],[1005,1117,"But now you expect me to keep"],[1117,1330,"my hands off of your dog too?!"],[1430,1572,"Leave Cookie out of this!"],[1572,1672,"He's a good dog."],[1672,1830,"Maybe Esther attacked him?"],[1830,2131,"You're blaming the bleeding child?"],[2131,2289,"This is unbelievable."],[2289,2431,"Stop!"],[2535,2723,"Fighting gets us nowhere."],[2723,2823,"What we should be doing"],[2823,2952,"is taking Esther to hospital."],[3069,3253,"Hey. You okay?"],[3253,3428,"Come with me."],[3628,3720,"You’ll be okay."],[3891,4024,"Oh huh."]],"51":[[133,250,"Oh, Mommy's here."],[250,346,"Mommy's here."],[713,996,"Oh! You psycho bitch!"],[996,1101,"You set a dog loose"],[1101,1217,"on my granddaughter."],[1217,1384,"I didn't do anything."],[1384,1559,"And Cookie doesn't bite people."],[1559,1647,"Why are you blaming him?"],[1647,1826,"You didn't even see what happened."],[1826,1885,"What do you think?"],[1885,2031,"My well-mannered granddaughter"],[2031,2202,"just started abusing the dog?"],[2235,2435,"That's ridiculous!"],[2435,2648,"With a mother like you,"],[2648,2927,"that baby's going to be the devil!"],[2927,3115,"Lord knows why Alec chose you"],[3115,3303,"to be the mother of his child."],[3303,3511,"You watch how you talk about, my child!"],[3511,3620,"Whether you like it or not,"],[3620,3795,"it has Lawrence blood."],[3795,3958,"You are lucky to have"],[3958,4137,"Alec's baby in your belly."],[4233,4521,"As for this violent dog of yours..."],[4521,4629,"It's got to go!"]],"52":[[0,108,"Not a chance!"],[108,321,"Cookie is family. He stays with me."],[321,567,"Either you ditch that dog,"],[567,738,"or both of you hit the road!"],[750,905,"If that little monster stays here"],[905,1038,"another minute,"],[1038,1163,"I'm calling the cops"],[1163,1338,"and telling them that your dog"],[1338,1555,"is a danger to society."],[1651,1868,"They'll euthanize him!"],[1868,2143,"No no no no. Give him back!"],[2143,2285,"Let him go. Okay, fine, I'll leave."],[2285,2389,"I'll leave like you ask. Please."],[2389,2577,"Just let him go. Don't hurt him."],[2577,2719,"That's what I thought."],[3103,3303,"Scram!"],[4166,4287,"When I heard Alec’s ex"],[4287,4383,"came back into town,"],[4383,4558,"I knew things would get messy."],[4579,4688,"Lucky for you Leia Gray..."],[4688,4808,"I just can't quit you."],[4867,5025,"I came in right after I got off the plane."],[5092,5213,"All right, let's get you out of this"],[5213,5392,"godforsaken place."],[5693,5876,"Of course she has another man."],[5922,6039,"Slut!"]],"53":[[650,813,"Uhh, Xavier..."],[813,900,"are you sure it's okay"],[900,1030,"that I stay here with you?"],[1034,1188,"Ever since Beatrice entered the picture,"],[1188,1247,"there's been a dozen"],[1247,1359,"media companies following"],[1359,1580,"the Lawrence family around 24/7."],[1609,1822,"Trust me, it's safer here."],[1822,1926,"But don't worry,"],[1926,2110,"I'll give you as much space as you need."],[2110,2339,"I’ve got plenty of extra room,"],[2339,2485,"come here--come pick one out."],[2752,2861,"Come on, Cookie,"],[2861,2907,"let's go."],[3791,3920,"Thanks, Alec."],[3920,4024,"Esther usually hates"],[4024,4145,"going to the doctor, but she was so"],[4145,4283,"much better with you there."],[4558,4688,"Where are you going?"],[4854,4971,"Beatrice..."],[4971,5155,"Leia and Cookie are innocent."],[5205,5342,"I only helped today"],[5342,5497,"because Esther got hurt."],[5497,5689,"If you treat Leia like that again,"],[5689,5868,"I'll have to ask you to leave my home."],[6268,6514,"Leia..."]],"54":[[129,241,"Leia?!"],[241,379,"That skank?"],[379,679,"She already ran off with Xavier."],[692,921,"I told you she was a bad egg."],[921,1201,"Did you say she left with Xavier?"],[1201,1338,"Once she found out that there was"],[1338,1497,"another family heiress"],[1509,1597,"that she wouldn't get a share"],[1597,1718,"of your fortune,"],[1793,2072,"she disappeared!"],[2419,2715,"Leia, where are you?"],[2715,2806,"Alec,"],[2806,2886,"you shouldn't be talking"],[2886,3015,"to me right now."],[3015,3228,"The situation with your ex and her kid"],[3228,3336,"and with our baby..."],[3336,3511,"it's--it's too messy."],[3511,3682,"Do you mean"],[3741,3983,"you want to break up?"],[4045,4099,"I think we should"],[4099,4312,"spend some time apart."],[4312,4408,"I'm sorry. Alec."]],"55":[[325,437,"Xavier,"],[437,563,"I’m not in the mood for this."],[563,684,"If you stay inside all day"],[684,804,"you’ll drive yourself crazy."],[804,871,"Come on! This is"],[871,1034,"the best restaurant in the city."],[1071,1317,"And the lobster risotto is to die for."],[1317,1518,"Oh my god, you guys are here too?"],[1614,1718,"What are the chances?"],[1718,1926,"Guess it’s a double-date!"],[2452,2686,"So, you’re really leaving me for him?"],[2752,2915,"Alec, I think it's best for everyone"],[2915,3053,"if you just get over Leia."],[3107,3232,"Don't you already have a daughter"],[3232,3282,"with Beatrice?"],[3282,3424,"How the fuck do you know"],[3424,3582,"about what’s best for everyone?"],[3591,3770,"All I know is you let her"],[3770,3832,"and her daughter"],[3832,4004,"come into your house and bully"],[4004,4175,"Leia in the middle of her pregnancy."],[4258,4429,"You don't deserve her!"],[4466,4596,"So you know that she’s pregnant"],[4596,4733,"with my child?"],[5150,5413,"Alec, let’s look at the menu first."],[5413,5509,"We still need to order"],[5509,5680,"the tiramisu for Esther."],[6001,6160,"Excuse me."],[6160,6452,"I have to go to the bathroom."]],"56":[[112,212,"Come on!"],[504,604,"Alec,"],[604,700,"let go of me."],[700,834,"If I let you go, you're gonna"],[834,1001,"go home with Xavier tonight."],[1001,1146,"Leia, I'm confused."],[1146,1259,"You told me you loved me,"],[1259,1372,"and now you're avoiding me."],[1372,1455,"What's going on?"],[1455,1747,"It's not a question of whether I love you."],[1747,1851,"You have a daughter"],[1851,1951,"with Beatrice,"],[1951,2156,"Your mother hates me with a passion."],[2185,2327,"I don't want to raise my baby"],[2327,2423,"in that kind of environment."],[2423,2598,"Fine! So let's run away together."],[2598,2711,"We can go anywhere you want."],[2711,2894,"Somewhere far away from here."],[2894,3044,"Look, I'm not going to let my mother"],[3044,3311,"get in between you, me, and this baby."],[3365,3545,"Alec,"],[3545,3745,"you don't get it."],[3745,3866,"You can't just..."],[3866,4004,"hide from your mother forever."],[4004,4137,"And you can't ignore"],[4137,4304,"your responsibility to your daughter."],[4371,4562,"Maybe..."],[4562,4675,"maybe it's best if..."],[4771,4996,"we're not together."],[4996,5146,"You don't mean it."],[5367,5463,"Leia?"],[5538,5830,"Leia, where are you?"],[5830,5914,"No,"],[5914,6068,"I'm not letting you leave with that man."],[6068,6172,"We have to be together."]],"57":[[25,325,"We have to be together."],[1534,1835,"Leia, is that you in there?"],[2181,2377,"Leia!"],[2723,3023,"Fuck! Alec..."],[3028,3128,"Fuck..."],[3128,3328,"You piece of shit!"],[3490,3620,"You forced yourself onto her."],[3620,3803,"You are the piece of shit, Xavier."],[3803,3887,"Keep your nose out of"],[3887,4045,"Leia’s and my relationship."],[4045,4183,"What relationship?"],[4183,4287,"You are the odd one out"],[4287,4441,"in this triangle."],[4441,4579,"Leia’s coming with me."],[4650,4900,"Alec..."],[4900,5050,"we're over."]],"58":[[33,87,"Xavier."],[321,504,"Uhm, thank you,"],[533,679,"for everything that you’ve done"],[679,817,"to help me. I really appreciate it."],[817,955,"But I don’t think I’m ready for another"],[955,1109,"relationship right now."],[1109,1176,"Leia,"],[1176,1380,"I’m not gonna ask you to be with me."],[1380,1547,"I just couldn't bear to see the girl"],[1547,1697,"I like getting treated that way."],[1697,1835,"I had to step in."],[1835,1981,"Xavier, I know..."],[1981,2097,"Unless you’re going to say that you"],[2097,2277,"feel the same way about me,"],[2277,2452,"I think you should get some sleep."],[2452,2752,"It's been a long day."],[4079,4216,"Damn."],[4216,4450,"Gotta get some groceries."]],"59":[[1009,1305,"You see that girl over there?"],[1305,1422,"Go rob her."],[1422,1543,"And while you're at it,"],[1543,1722,"rough her up a little bit."],[1985,2097,"If I could get Leia"],[2097,2206,"to have a miscarriage"],[2206,2377,"then the Lawrence family fortune"],[2377,2548,"will be all mine!"],[3211,3645,"Oh. Oh. Oh."],[3703,3974,"Oh. Oh, my baby!"],[3974,4300,"Oh, no! Oh!"],[4437,4537,"Hi. Uh yes,"],[4537,4675,"I’m by the intersection of"],[4675,4909,"Third Street and Center Avenue."],[4938,5146,"A pregnant woman has been attacked."],[5146,5330,"Please send someone quick!"]],"60":[[342,558,"Dear God,"],[558,829,"please let Leia be okay."],[829,996,"You can punish me however You want,"],[996,1230,"just let her be okay."],[1230,1572,"Alec, I heard Leia got attacked."],[1572,1689,"Is she all right?"],[1689,1893,"I don't know, they're still treating her."],[1893,2085,"Oh, poor Leia,"],[2085,2256,"I really hope the baby survives."],[2344,2473,"Don't worry, Alec,"],[2473,2627,"even if she loses a baby,"],[2627,2865,"we still have our beautiful daughter."],[2865,2927,"Daddy,"],[2927,3140,"I don't want a bastard sibling."],[3294,3503,"That is no way for a six year old to talk."],[3503,3645,"Did you teach her that?"],[3645,3841,"Alec, don't be upset."],[3841,3970,"You know what they say--"],[3970,4104,"start ‘em young!"],[4104,4225,"Excuse me."],[4225,4429,"Are you Mr. Lawrence?"],[4429,4508,"Yes."],[4508,4579,"This is your daughter's"],[4579,4700,"health report--"],[4700,4796,"you forgot to take it with you"],[4796,4842,"the last time"],[4842,4975,"you brought her here."],[4975,5092,"Thank you."]],"61":[[183,346,"Both of our blood type is-"],[346,533,"type O."],[533,684,"Esther’s is type A."],[834,1042,"She's not my daughter, is she?"],[1088,1222,"This is a mistake."],[1222,1347,"Don't you remember"],[1347,1480,"the DNA test I showed you?"],[1480,1618,"Steve isn’t my daddy!"],[1618,1714,"You are."],[1818,2064,"Steve?"],[2064,2189,"I want you and this girl"],[2189,2406,"out of my house immediately."],[2448,2627,"If you're still there when I get home,"],[2627,2815,"I will throw you out with my own hands."],[2815,3003,"Do you understand me?"],[3636,3891,"Doc, how is she doing?"],[3891,4116,"I'm sorry, sir. Your wife, she..."]],"62":[[25,116,"I'm sorry. Sir."],[116,291,"Your wife, she-- What is it?"],[291,479,"Tell me! -Sir, relax!"],[479,658,"The baby's going to make it."],[658,880,"Ms. Gray is just very tired right now."],[880,955,"And we need to keep her"],[955,1051,"a few more weeks."],[1051,1146,"Okay."],[1626,1797,"Leia!"],[1797,1893,"It's okay."],[1893,2193,"The baby's going to be okay."],[2289,2389,"Get some rest."],[2389,2489,"We can talk it all over"],[2489,2690,"when you're feeling better."],[2919,3119,"So Beatrice's ex,"],[3119,3278,"who went broke and fled the country"],[3278,3586,"is actually Esther's father?"]],"63":[[16,191,"That's right."],[191,367,"Beatrice was living like a queen,"],[367,567,"and then all their money vanished."],[567,704,"She heard about me and"],[704,871,"hatched a plan to"],[871,1013,"steal my inheritance."],[1276,1505,"Seeing as I just got swindled,"],[1505,1618,"is there any way you could find"],[1618,1805,"a way to forgive me?"],[1818,2035,"I promise that if I ever let anything"],[2035,2335,"happen to you or our child again,"],[2473,2677,"I will give you every penny I have,"],[2677,2977,"and I will leave you alone forever."],[3203,3503,"Oh, fine."],[3541,3707,"But just so you know,"],[3707,3866,"the only reason that I'm forgiving you"],[3866,4166,"is because of your cooking skills."],[4379,4562,"Also,"],[4562,4729,"when my Mom found out"],[4729,4896,"that Esther wasn't my child,"],[4896,5013,"she lost her shit"],[5013,5251,"and kicked Beatrice out of the house."],[5251,5330,"She said..."],[5392,5568,"when you get out of the hospital,"],[5568,5672,"she wants to apologize"],[5672,5797,"to you personally."],[5939,6035,"Do you think you could"],[6035,6239,"forgive her as well?"],[6389,6514,"If not, it's okay."],[6514,6631,"We can ..."],[6631,6815,"move somewhere far away."],[6890,7023,"But I promise you,"],[7023,7161,"she doesn't hold any animosity"],[7161,7520,"towards you or the child anymore."],[7520,7841,"If she's genuinely"],[7895,8187,"sorry and wants to make amends,"],[8187,8337,"then I can forgive her."],[8425,8625,"She is your mother, after all."]],"64":[[95,233,"Two balloons?!"],[233,458,"That means twins."],[592,792,"All right. Are you guys ready?"],[821,950,"Yeah, we’re ready."],[988,1121,"Time for the countdown."],[1180,1459,"3... 2... 1!"],[3228,3399,"Oh... my god!"],[3399,3528,"Oh my god, triplets?"],[3632,3749,"Triplets?!"],[3749,3870,"I can't believe Alec"],[3870,4020,"didn't tell me sooner!"],[4020,4195,"Oh my God. Wasn't everybody saying"],[4195,4325,"how Leia’s infertile?"],[4325,4521,"Now she's having three babies!"],[4521,4637,"The Lawrences don't have to worry"],[4637,4833,"about their family fortune now."],[4833,4942,"They have three kids"],[4942,5138,"to choose an heir or heiress from!"],[5138,5238,"Triplets!"],[5238,5426,"What incredible luck!"],[5622,5801,"Okay."],[5801,5901,"3..."],[5901,6081,"2... 1"],[6631,6823,"Congrats to these two lovebirds."],[6823,7044,"But, Leia, if you ever"],[7044,7148,"get bored of Alec,"],[7236,7499,"you know where to find me."],[7499,7615,"One second..."],[7615,7799,"No, you dummy!"],[7799,7945,"Come here."],[8083,8229,"(I love you.)"]]}